description:
What can i add to the myriad of reviews already offered?   Well I would say this is almost the epitome of the SF Cafe . . . an here is why I love places like this:
:: Makes be feel local even though I drive across town to go;
:: Makes me feel "down" because all the artsy kewl kidz are hanging out;
:: Doesn't make be feel too "down" because I still pay too much money for things;
:: Makes me feel like I am in Europe because most of the people there are or want me to think they are;
:: Can sit outside and feel even more European, Parisian even;
:: Blue Danube, you had me at WiFi.
